S.FORM: == moy == 九節木 u siwkay nu lalidec yadah ku ciid tina kilang. manah tu dihku malalemeday a demiad. mauzip i cayka takalaway a takalaw nu bayu'. akenek ku sanek. taneng pasapayu'.anu makanmaw, adad' ku ngipen, mabanic, adada' ku tusuc atu ukak, maduka, makalad nu cilekay, taneng mukan tina kilang a sapayu'. kilang-takalaw sa 2m, papah 13-18cm tanaya', 5-6cm ahebal. sibalu i 5-6 a bulad. u heci sa sumanahay. kibetul ku pudac nu heci. . u siwkay nu nipaluma u sanek nu nipaluma malaheci tu imelang pasubana i cacudadan a lacul u zuma a cidekay a kamu, saungay misapayu' a cidekay u sulit nu zuma a kamu-Hulam atu Amilika u sulit nu Hulam 九節(學名:Psychotria rubra), .

== moy == 九節木 o siwkay no lalidec yadah ko ciid tina kilang. manah to dihko malalemeday a demiad. maozip i cayka takalaway a takalaw no bayo'. akenek ko sanek. taneng pasapayo'.ano makanmaw, adad' ko ngipen, mabanic, adada' ko tosoc ato okak, madoka, makalad no cilekay, taneng mokan tina kilang a sapayo'. kilang-takalaw sa 2m, papah 13-18cm tanaya', 5-6cm ahebal. sibalo i 5-6 a bolad. o heci sa somanahay. kibetol ko podac no heci. . o siwkay no nipaloma o sanek no nipaloma malaheci to imelang pasobana i cacodadan a lacol o zoma a cidekay a kamo, saongay misapayo' a cidekay o solit no zoma a kamo-Holam ato Amilika o solit no Holam 九節(學名:Psychotria robra), .
